Consistency: $ V_{\text{pred}} $ calculated as $ V_1 + V_2 + 2 \rho_{12} \sqrt{V_1 V_2} + \mathrm{CF} \cdot \exp(-|\rho_{12}/0.06|^2) $ with $ \mathrm{CF} = 0.003 $.
$ \Omega_{\text{pred}} $: $ \lambda_{\Omega} \approx 1.0 $, adjusted for anti-aligned pairs.
Noise: $ V_{\text{obs}} = V_{\text{pred}} + \epsilon $, $ \Omega_{\text{obs}} = \Omega_{\text{pred}} + \epsilon $, $ \epsilon \sim \mathcal{N}(0, 0.001) $.
Tolerances: $ \tau_V = 2.33 \cdot 0.0018 \approx 0.0042 $, $ \tau_{\Omega} = 2.33 \cdot 0.0010 \approx 0.0023 $, $ \tau_{\Omega,0} = 2.0 \cdot 0.0010 = 0.0020 $, all passed.



