Near-Zero (IDs 1–10): $ r_V $ values (0.001 or 0.002) yield MAD ≈ 0.0015, matching $ \hat{\sigma}_{V,0} $ for CF.
All Regimes (IDs 1–30): $ r_V $ (0.001–0.002) SD ≈ 0.0018 ($ \hat{\sigma}_V $), $ r_{\Omega} $ (0.000–0.002) SD ≈ 0.0010 ($ \hat{\sigma}_{\Omega} $).


Refit $ \lambda_{\Omega} $:

Anti-Aligned (IDs 11–30): $ \Omega_{\text{obs}} \approx \Omega_{\text{pred}} $ within $ 10^{-3} $, least-squares slope ≈ 1.0000 (R² ≈ 1.0), confirming $ \lambda_{\Omega} = 1.0000 $.


Compute Tolerances:

$ \tau_V = 2.33 \cdot 0.0018 \approx 0.0042 $.
$ \tau_{\Omega} = 2.33 \cdot 0.0010 \approx 0.0023 $.
$ \tau_{\Omega,0} = 2.0 \cdot 0.0010 = 0.0020 $.
$ \mathrm{CF} = 2 \cdot 0.0015 = 0.0030 $.


